  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kick Bastards is a parkour game with a heavy focus on varied and expressive movement. You will be pushed to master the deep movement systems to overcome varied and difficult challenges.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/1ec9e50458b8eac25330304997632940.poster.avif?t=1757596717\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/1ec9e50458b8eac25330304997632940.webm?t=1757596717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/764fef67762b238dd11786852d6974d0.webp?t=1757596717\" width=616 height=35 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You messed up. You’re in Hell and you ain’t too happy about it. Use all your cunning and parkour skills to escape the Devil as he chases you across dimensions. Over 70+ you will have to fight back against the armies of Hell and fulfil your destiny.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/3e919a7983b4f0b6b6a429713584c54c.poster.avif?t=1757596717\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/3e919a7983b4f0b6b6a429713584c54c.webm?t=1757596717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/6fcf6f433598cbd1c1b8be585ec84ba3.webp?t=1757596717\" width=616 height=35 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go outrageously fast! There is NO CAP on your speed so you can go crazy fast by cleverly combo-ing your moves together. Kick Bastards features real world parkour moves as well as super fun fantastical elements that are combined together to create a rich and exciting movement system.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/69d3dd12e63a32863dee3682fc91f2f9.poster.avif?t=1757596717\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/69d3dd12e63a32863dee3682fc91f2f9.webm?t=1757596717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/ce2a60e6ffbc9690744101df8c56cbb4.webp?t=1757596717\" width=616 height=35 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ultimate kicking simulation!! That’s right you kick stuff in the game called Kick Bastards. In fact you will kick a lot of stuff, so much stuff. All your kicking fantasies will be satisfied.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/302f1f1b25623a6dc25cbb17e86680c8.poster.avif?t=1757596717\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/302f1f1b25623a6dc25cbb17e86680c8.webm?t=1757596717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/ec120f58d7fe6b3dbd14155b99adba00.webp?t=1757596717\" width=616 height=35 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What’s better than a hard fought win, it feels amazing to push yourself to the limit to achieve greatness. In every level you’ll get hooked into collecting medals and maybe even fighting for the top spot on the leaderboards.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/8e9ae35b42d753473a5e55a144cb495d.poster.avif?t=1757596717\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/8e9ae35b42d753473a5e55a144cb495d.webm?t=1757596717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/09210d30e42142819d70e24961e79f5d.webp?t=1757596717\" width=616 height=35 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you have worked your way through the 70+ levels in the game you’ll find yourself getting hooked on the two additional game modes: 'Spider-person mode', you get a grappling hook that attaches anywhere and lets you swing around all the levels like the Spider-guy himself. Additionally there is 'Super Kick mode' which asks the question ‘What if your kick is so unreasonably powerful that you can basically fly around the sky at high speeds like some kind of bird that kicks things a lot?’.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kick Bastards is a parkour game with a heavy focus on varied and expressive movement. You will be pushed to master the deep movement systems to overcome varied and difficult challenges.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/1ec9e50458b8eac25330304997632940.poster.avif?t=1757596717\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/1ec9e50458b8eac25330304997632940.webm?t=1757596717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/764fef67762b238dd11786852d6974d0.webp?t=1757596717\" width=616 height=35 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You messed up. You’re in Hell and you ain’t too happy about it. Use all your cunning and parkour skills to escape the Devil as he chases you across dimensions. Over 70+ you will have to fight back against the armies of Hell and fulfil your destiny.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/3e919a7983b4f0b6b6a429713584c54c.poster.avif?t=1757596717\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/3e919a7983b4f0b6b6a429713584c54c.webm?t=1757596717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737400/extras/6fcf6f433598cbd1c1b8be585ec84ba3.webp?t=1757596717\" width=616 height